gr.forth.ics.jbenchy.diagram.gnuplot
Class PlotStyle

java.lang.Object
  gr.forth.ics.jbenchy.diagram.gnuplot.PlotStyle

public class PlotStyle
extends java.lang.Object

Defines a style for drawing datasets in gnuplot. Specifically, models the gnuplot language part which supports phrases like "with points" , "with linespoints pointstyle 7", etc. Use the static factory methods to create predefines styles, or subclass to make a new style not supported here.

Author:
andreou
